<div class="com-share" data-id="6891" data-title="《GAP任命的新设计总监，来自维多利亚的秘密》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6891/medium/6891.jpg?1436697423" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6891.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
